Quote:
Order 7, Rule 11 of CPC 11. Rejection of plaint - The plaint shall be rejected in the C/FA/5349/2019 JUDGMENT following cases : [d] Where the suit appears from the statement in the plaint to be barred by any law;
Sec.17[1], Sec.18 and Sec.19[6 to 11] of the Recovery of Debts and Bankruptcy Act.
